	returns at least some decimal places more often than not.

2006-02-12  Derek Atkins  <derek@ihtfp.com>

	* src/business/*/*.scm:
	  rename gnc:owner-get-address-dep to
	  gnc:owner-get-name-and-address-dep in preparation of
	  some other patches.

